{\listtext	\'95	}1 jalapeno, finely diced\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 cloves garlic, finely chopped\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons ancho chili powder\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 teaspoon ground coriander\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 to 2 chipotle peppers in adobo, processed until smooth\
{\listtext	\'95	}One 28-ounce can plum tomatoes and their juice, processed until smoothKosher salt and freshly ground black pepper\
{\listtext	\'95	}Clover honey, to taste, optional\
