{\listtext	\'95	}1/3 pound chuck, very cold, cubed\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/3 pound pork butt, very cold, cubed 3 cloves garlic, finely chopped\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 large egg, lightly beaten\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup finely chopped cilantro, plus extra for garnish\
